modules are not transitive; prefer APIs or XHTML5 paths available from the resolved artifact unless deliberately adding such test dependencies later.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Existing 1.9.1 tests use removed methods/classes such as RenderingContext, SkinResourceLoader, enableLogging, and setUsingDefaultTemplate.\",\n    \"Directly constructing DefaultSiteRenderer is only safe for methods that do not touch injected collaborators; full render/locate flows need proper collaborator initialization.\",\n    \"APT/XDoc/FML parser modules appear as upstream test-scope dependencies, not runtime transitives, so tests that require those parsers would need explicit dependencies.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0be56e4e92dbc717016a3f4593623c81938228c1606361ba6f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1090, "output": 1494, "cacheRead": 36864, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 39448, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782531459524, "responseId": "resp_0be56e4e92dbc717016a3f45842a3881938600976da555aab9"}, "toolResults": []}
